Quickstrike:




Quickstrike jerked his head and paused. "They left me that's what 
happened," he replied to Black Arachnia through his comm-link. "We 
won 'gainst th' Maxis. They retreated while our slaggin' team ran off 
like th' tin-horns they are. Ah don't know where Dark Mouse is. Ah 
don't remember seein' her there."
